name: The Hunger From The Stars
description:
A butcher of human flesh, this extraterrestrial creature looks like your average human girl, but underneath her malleable, shapeshifting flesh, lies a deadly predator, the Queen of Meat. From what dark star or corrupted world it came is unknown, but we all can pray that there are no more of these predators lurking in the inky blackness of space. 

The Hunger From the Stars is an illustration used for the cover of the book "Tender Morsels" by Rick Kitagawa.
